    {
      "chinese": "清安村傳統部落稱為「Mabatu’an」，漢名清安村，舊名馬都安社，本為番社名。該地散居大湖溪上游右岸和洗水溪（清安溪）上游左岸，因而得名。遠來本地洗水溪線開墾的客家人，泛稱本區為洗水坑。",
      "ab": "Cingancun ga capaang na ralu’ cu’ cunga’ ga Mabatu’an. kaykian ka hani ga, maghaghap i’ raya’ nku’ tigianan na gawng na Tayku’ ru raya’ nku’ tigiil na gawng na Mayhing. kiya ku’ minuwah cku’ tatuhi ka cuquliq ka Siputu’, muwah ’i’ minang cku’ gawng na Mayhing. yani san maha’ kaykian i’ Sisuweikeng.",
